chunk_content: Identify the level of engagement in PT activities for each laboratory-based testing site by choosing one of the following: • Performs this test but does not participate in PT (see definition of “PT participation” below). • Performs this test and participates in PT. Sum the number of specimens received for testing at all POCT sites within a testing category. See definition for “specimens received for testing.” How are data interpreted and reported (Point-of-Care Testing)? Identify the level of engagement in CQI activities for each POCT site by choosing one of the following: • Performs this test but does not participate in CQI. • Performs this test, participates in CQI, but has not been fully certified/accredited. • Performs this test, participates in CQI, and has been fully certified/accredited.
